Alexander Bradley testified at Aaron Hernandez's murder trial on Wednesday . 
  Bradley says he was Hernandez's former drug dealer and then his best friend . 
  He will be allowed to testify that Hernandez had access to a black Glock pistol in a Miami hotel . 
  But he cannot reveal that he claims Hernandez shot him in the face in 2013 . 
  Hernandez is accused of killing semipro football player Odin Lloyd . 
  He appeared in court on Wednesday to decide what he could testify about . 
  Bradley said he can testify about the pistol but not about a separate 2013 incident . 
 